4 April 2026 - 1:50 PM I&rsquo;m a little uncomfortable with committing small changes&hellip;
maybe i should think about domain name and servers.

Hello World! This is Yasan, I am 22 y.o computer engineering student at Politecnico di Torino.
I really like animations (more than movies!) and Open source world (Thanks to Linus Torvalds&lt;3)
I made 3D animations and characters before - because I like to create things - but these days I&rsquo;m changing my creation field. Struggling with 0 and 1s :)
and codes&hellip;
and semi-colons&hellip;
